snippet.title: SINNER: Sacrifice for Redemption Launch Date Trailer
snippet.description:
Sinner: Sacrifice for Redemption is coming to Nintendo Switch, PlayStation 4 and Xbox One on October 18!

It will also come to Discord as a First on Discord launch title later this year, with Steam to follow after that.
 
Join the Discord: https://discord.gg/ai
more info https://anotherindie.com
 
Wishlist on Steam: 
https://store.steampowered.com/app/691280/SINNER_Sacrifice_for_Redemption/
